This paper focuses on the communication of robot motion intent to humans, which is a topic that falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also involves the use of mixed reality head-mounted displays, which is a technology that falls under the category of computer graphics (cs.GR) and computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper involves the use of robotics (cs.RO) and image recognition (cs.IR) to evaluate the effectiveness of the proposed system.
